ToDo App

User can do the following:

1. Login to server and get Token (JWT token) - { POST /login }
2. Get ToDo List - { GET /todo }
3. Create a ToDo - { POST /todo }
4. Delete a Todo by id - { DELETE /todo }

Installation Steps:

1. Install MySQL database by referring the `.sql` file in directory named `database`
2. To run test cases: `npm run test`
3. To run server: `npm run server`

Below mentioned the link for postman collection to access APIs:

Link: https://www.getpostman.com/collections/63320c4e8a9b65b1381f

Note: Postman Test cases has also been written, which will store the JWT token after envoking "/login" API.
